                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>A creature hit by the animated wardrobe's clothes whip becomes @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Grabbed] by the animated wardrobe. The creature isn't @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Immobilized], but it can't move beyond the reach of the wardrobe's clothes whip. A creature can sever the clothes whip with a Strike against AC 15 that deals at least 5 slashing damage. This deals no damage to the animated wardrobe.</p>"
